7 Giant Eagle (No tile)
Difficulty 31
Attacks

Claw 4d4 physical, Claw 4d4 physical, Bite 3d8 physical, Gaze attack 2d6 blinding

Base level 25
Base experience 1088
Speed 24
Base AC −20
Base MR 100
Alignment 20 (lawful)
Frequency (by normal means) 0 (Not randomly generated)
Genocidable No
Weight 3000
Nutritional value 800
Size huge
Resistances fire, cold, sleep, shock, poison, level drain
Resistances conveyed sleep

A Giant Eagle:

  • can fly.
  • is an animal.
  • regenerates HP quickly.
  • can see invisible creatures.
  • does not eat. (*)
  • is not a valid polymorphable form.
  • is a lord to its kind.
  • can follow you to other levels.
  • is nasty.
  • is strong.
  • can pick up weapons and food.
  • can pick up magical items.
  • can be seen through infravision.
  • does not appear in Gehennom.
  • resists level drain.
  • cannot be tamed.

Giant Eagles are powerful divine beings that may be found on the Planes in dNetHack.
